org.apache.ignite.tests.p2p

Class GridExternalAffinityFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.tests.p2p.GridExternalAffinityFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AffinityFunction

    public class GridExternalAffinityFunction
extends Object
implements AffinityFunction
    Mock affinity implementation that ensures constant key-to-node mapping based on GridCacheModuloAffinity The partition selection is as follows: 0 maps to partition 1 and any other value maps to partition 1.
